  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dca\u0d9a\u0dd2 \u0dba\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d9a\u0da7\u0dd4\u0db1\u0dcf\u0dba\u0d9a\u0daf\u0dd3 \u0d85\u0db1\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0d9a",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A Turkish plane is in an accident in Katunayake",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A Turkish Airlines cargo plane, which was about to take off, has crashed at the Katunayake airport due to strong winds.",
        "This is an A.-330-300 Airbus cargo plane belonging to Turkish Airlines.",
        "This plane had arrived at Katunayake Airport with cargo from Istanbul, Turkey.",
        "After that, this plane was preparing to depart from Katunayake Airport for Istanbul, Turkey, carrying a load of clothes made by \"Victoria's Secret Stores\", weighing 45 metric tons.",
        "At that time, due to the strong wind conditions at Katunayake Airport and its surrounding area, a container that had been brought to be loaded onto this aircraft, was parked near the relevant aircraft by the Sri Lankan Airlines airport operators without applying the brakes properly. This accident has happened when it was swept towards the plane and collided with its engine.",
        "Therefore, the necessary steps have not been taken by the Turkish aviation authorities to restore the engine damaged by the accident or to leave the Katunayake airport."
      ],
